Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经很懦弱的 Yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.75,0:00:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很想大哭一场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以气馁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论何时也不是孤独一人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遥远的梦想在闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将它找回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.70,0:00:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把双眼闭上便可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.67,0:00:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在心中的一个角落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算留下伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.88,0:00:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要害怕 现在是两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:01:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放弃 Step by Step
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓着梦想 Your Fight Jump
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经常也和你一起向明天迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.77,0:01:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续前进 Step by Step
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想坚信着 Your Fight Jump
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.71,0:01:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想向着天空大声呼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃烧着 in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.39,0:01:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫战部渡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了打倒支配着遥远星界山的多坏达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.49,0:01:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再次成为救世主,展开了冒险旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.07,0:01:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二星界是有趣的冒险世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里我们要把被沙漠化了的世界恢复原本翠绿的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.20,0:01:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在查依鲁村被巨鸟抢了星石的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.71,0:01:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发了去找回星石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:02:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也会是"超"有趣又有型
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第十话\N和像一起去找星石
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把星石还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.94,0:02:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不听我的话便把你烤来吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.27,0:02:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也不怕吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅,你再认真点追啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.48,0:02:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事想到食物也不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且有人比我更不认真
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸟先生,我来追你了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.41,0:02:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂!火美子,你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.63,0:02:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,真失晕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.89,0:02:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再慢吞吞便丢下你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.52,0:03:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是谁,在这里掘洞啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.64,0:03:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个第二星界有我曾哥里亚大人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只需一会便变成沙漠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的树,沙漠是不需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么忙的时候到底是谁啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星界第一的大力士,曾哥里亚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头子!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该叫我力量最大才对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂,我知道了,你冷静点…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的,叫大力士不是一样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是曾哥里亚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发挥你的力量的时候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只鸟抢了渡的星石逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要比他们快点找出星石
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你的力量把它粉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话,这个第二星界便会永远变成沙漠了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.01,0:04:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了,交给我曾哥里亚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是不要再叫我做头子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的,头子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不理什么星石也好,什么也好,都会变成这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅,真的是真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我说多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的确是看见那鸟停了在这山崖上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会看错了吧,你眼力不是衰退了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我没见你的一段时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你变得说话很尖酸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很大的鸟儿在上面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅,赶快吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧,我说的话没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是今次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.76,0:05:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了,跟着怎样接近星石呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.50,0:05:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么人?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道他也想取星石?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你便是渡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这星界第一的大力士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾哥里亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽然很喜欢吃荞头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但乌东我也很喜欢 (近音:大力士)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不,更正
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是星界第一力量最大的曾哥里亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,你要葬身于此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉悟吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐,你是多坏达的手下吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,让我轻轻松松地收拾你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:45.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对渡来说太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然二对一是违反武士道精神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这时候没法子了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野牛武一郎流,梦幻的右直拳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师…师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见面不如闻名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.82,0:07:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么今次到我了,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是什么怪力?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才真危险呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.33,0:07:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是爷爷,曾哥里亚那家伙得到教训了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已为了找水源,进行了很长的旅程了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫乌间达,这孩子叫波古
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后这巨大的象叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾利芬,是这星界中最巨大的生物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.11,0:08:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初看见时真吓了一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓得灵魂也飞了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.12,0:08:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾利芬有一种能找出水源的神奇力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然有这样的能力,为何会进行了长久的旅程?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来一言难尽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前只要掘的话,水源四处也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾利芬也能简单的找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全靠它,我们筑起围棚养猪牛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:09:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青草也不会少去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾利芬给予我们水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相对的我们种植
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾利芬的量食佐加利树给它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相方互利互益的生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是,因为那个曾哥里亚的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令这里变成了沙漠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是水,连佐加利树也激灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去艾利芬会饿死的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是罪无可恕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对,如果取回星石的话便有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?你说星石?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是,但是被一只巨大的鸟抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷,巨大的鸟会不会是奥巴鸟?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话,它去的便是犀之河原了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西之河原!?(同音)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为…为什么会到西之河原…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:10:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥巴鸟到了这个季节便会到犀之河原生蛋的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?那么在那里埋伏的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就这样向犀之河原出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾利芬被两边山崖夹住了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行,完全打不碎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅,你那边怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边的墙也很硬不能破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:11:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅,没有其他办法吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只有你们,也请去犀之河原吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有星石的话,便能让这星界恢复原状吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么现在便要把此事看得最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猪先生 猪先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是不能这样放着艾利芬不管的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这样下去什么办法也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的力量不能令艾利芬活动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猪先生 猪先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子,好吵啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在弄痒猪先生的鼻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今次到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:11:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,你到底打算怎么做?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡打算用那个弄痒艾利芬的鼻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对,利用艾利芬打喷嚏时的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了,艾利芬打个大喷嚏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我弄痒艾利芬的鼻时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾利芬便会打喷嚏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:33.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话,那力量便会把我吹走…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,超了不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来渡呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾…艾利芬呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧,已拔出山崖了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾利芬说多谢你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太…太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里便是犀之河原吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是有很多犀牛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以便叫犀之河原吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,大家躲在崖石后面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样才可以不被那鸟发现接近呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍法,岩石龟之术
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.99,0:14:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样便能不被它发现的接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此,龟能隐身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得好,火美子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢地,慢慢地去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:15:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油,加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾…曾哥里亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要在你们面前,把这星石打至粉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:33.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾哥里亚,我不会再把星石给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你们集合了多少人,我也能一个一个的收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.27,0:15:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来吧,死亡土人!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.45,0:16:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这部死亡土人把你们全部杀掉,我来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾利芬,把曾哥里亚那家伙打飞!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.88,0:16:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是体形较大罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.95,0:16:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾利芬!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.94,0:16:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾哥里亚,今次到龙神丸做你对手了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才不是死亡土人的对手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会输的!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比力量的话,我不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也叫做力量吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.31,0:17:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量是这样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,艾利芬,包扎完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了,星石我拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.22,0:18:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不老实交出来的话,便会被这支矛穿过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒绝!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.89,0:18:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算要了在下的命,也不会把星石给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你便死吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.10,0:18:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来被我打倒吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么便这样吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛苦吧,痛苦吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾…艾利芬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了,渡 !
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动也动不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样刺死你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.58,0:19:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸,振作点!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行,身体动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得好,小艾利芬!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.19,0:19:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你,艾利芬,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,我出来了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便不会让你有命回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.87,0:19:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好,另一部魔神出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.35,0:19:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下去叫战神丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子你看守着星石吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁?竟突然攻击我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.27,0:19:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心你说话的态度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他便是这个星界的头子,法鲁战王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.26,0:20:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法鲁战王?那么那家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二星界的波士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾哥里亚,不要说多余的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快收拾渡,抢回星石吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.13,0:20:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这句话应该是我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢,竟向我攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟…糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈祷吧,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.78,0:20:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你的末日了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法…法鲁战王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧,龙神丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.45,0:20:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙雷拳!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体麻痹了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候了,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.54,0:21:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必杀!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星龙剑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有力量是不行的!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟反抗我,真有胆色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别以为可以就此算…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法鲁战王!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今次到你了,和我决胜负吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战神丸也参战!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还是先撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.10,0:21:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我记着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.63,0:21:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那部绿色的魔神到底是什么人?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.30,0:21:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.78,0:21:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星石也取回了,之后只剩下到基拿基拿山了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.01,0:21:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.16,0:22:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说多谢的话没有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.07,0:22:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也一起去基拿基拿山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.80,0:22:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想一定可以帮到你们手的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.00,0:22:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样便太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.51,0:22:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小艾利芬,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.20,0:22:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了? 这个胸口在驱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.57,0:22:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蹦蹦在跳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.67,0:22:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop! 已不能停止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.56,0:22:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连你也一个劲儿地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.41,0:22:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,油门不用放开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.66,0:22:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直踏着 Go!Go!Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.78,0:22:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流星也不能代替
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.82,0:23:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是速度的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.06,0:23:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,TONIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.76,0:23:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密的旋律笨拙的舞蹈 Dancin'
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.81,0:23:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够抱到她的心 LUCKY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直望着的瞳孔涌上了 HAPPY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.13,0:23:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是 MY GIRL
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.35,0:23:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今夜 MY LOVE

